Project Setup

Configure your Kodex documentation project

Project Selection

Enter the path to your project folder

Model Configuration

Select the AI model to use for generating documentation

If not provided, the ANTHROPIC_API_KEY environment variable will be used

Agent Context

Provide custom instructions to guide the agent during codebase analysis

These instructions help the AI understand your product context and generate more relevant documentation

Exclusion Patterns

Specify areas of the codebase to skip during analysis (one pattern per line)

Use glob patterns to exclude files and directories. Common patterns include test files, legacy code, and generated files.

Output Location

Generated documentation will be saved to the project folder

This location is automatically set based on your project path
